snippet.description:

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

snippet.title: Jaanam | Bad Newz | Vicky Kaushal | Triptii Dimri | Vishal Mishra | In cinemas 19th July
snippet.description:
After the first song 'Tauba Tauba' from the film Bad Newz now experience the magic of love with "Jaanam," where the charismatic Vicky Kaushal and Triptii Dimri set the screen on fire with their breathtaking chemistry. This romantic song sung by Vishal Mishra is a perfect blend of heartfelt emotions and visual splendor, making it a must-watch for all music lovers.

👉 Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Credits:
Composer : Vishal Mishra
Singer : Vishal Mishra
Lyrics : Vishal Mishra
All Music Produced Arranged & Designed By : Vishal Mishra
Music Assistants : Kumar Gaurav Singh & Trihangku Lahkar
Additional Female Vocals - Shreya Jain
Music Supervisor : Azeem Dayani
Associate Music Supervisor : Manish Natekar
Mixed and Mastered by : Eric Pillai @ Future Sound of Bombay
Recording Engineer @VM Studio : Trihangku Lahkar
Song editor - Nitin FCP
Assistant Song Editor - Mahesh Bhojwani
Choreographer : Remo D’souza

Bad Newz in cinemas 19th July.
Amazon Prime presents
In association with Dharma Productions and Leo Media Collective
A Leo Media Collective production
BAD NEWZ
Starring Vicky Kaushal, Triptii Dimri and Ammy Virk
Directed by Anand Tiwari
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Apoorva Mehta, Amritpal Singh Bindra & Anand
Tiwari
Written by Ishita Moitra & Tarun Dudeja

Lyrics:
Naina banjaron mein
Mushkilen aa baithi hain
Ishq bechaini ki
Ye talab la baithi hain

Aise na yun dekho dekho jaanam
Aise na yun dekho jaanam
Hona jayein hum bhi tere jaanam
Aise na yun dekho jaanam

Oo..

Hmm...
Kabhi aankhon se ye bayaan kare meri aadatein
Dil hai mera ab bezubaan teri raah take
Jaise humdum mile
Kaise hardum mile
Itni haseen ho phir
Ye saadgi hai kaise

Aasma mera hai
Dil jo ye tera hai
Ud raha main hadein tode

Dil pe aye janeja
Dhun teri aa baithi hai
Oo
Ishq bechaini ki
Ye talab la baithi hai

Aise na yun dekho dekho jaanam
Aise na yun dekho jaanam
Hona jaaye hum bhi tere jaanam
Aise na yun dekho jaanam

Oo

Ishq hade tere naam kare
Aur saans saans tere naam kare
Humdum mere humdum mere janaam
Mere janaam
Ishq hade tere naam kare
Aur saans saans iljaam kare
Humdum mere humdum mere jaanam

Ye talab la bethi hai
Ye talab la bethi hai
Ishq bechaini ki ye
Zindagi ka bethi hai
Dekho dekho jaanam
Aise na yun dekho jaanam

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
It’s 200x faster than a human as long as you don’t include the 3 years it took to build it. Hack Pack is a DIY robot subscription box that’s perfect for teens and adults with no coding experience required! Get 1 free box at http://crunchlabs.com/puzzle

نوجوانان و بزرگسالان اکنون می‌توانند مهارت‌های مهندسی خلاقانه خود را ارتقا دهند و ربات خود را در کنار من بسازند: http://crunchlabs.com/puzzle

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4136: Popatlal Gayab Hain
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal goes missing on his engagement day, and Inspector Pandey holds the Gokuldham members responsible for his disappearance. The entire community is in turmoil, asking themselves where Popatlal is and whether he will show up for his engagement.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4136 | 13 July 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1000282777

snippet.title: சூறாவளி புயல் in our Garden | Steffi Vlog in Tamil
snippet.description:
Our garden has suffered some damage during the recent weather events. A lot of broken branches from nearby trees have damaged our small plants. Strong winds have also bent several trees and thrown debris all our our backyard. We have tried to salvage all we could and we are fixing things over the next few weeks.
#steffiulagam #steffigarden

Friends, hope you liked today's vlog and see you soon with more interesting videos. Also, I hope you will find some inspiration to grow some plants and home and spread the joy of gardening in the face of all challenges.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Eating The BEST BURGER For 24 Hours Challenge 🍔🔥
snippet.description:
Welcome to FoodieWe, your ultimate guide to finding the best burger in India! Join our passionate food explorers Onkar, Mukti, and Aditya as they embark on a mouth-watering journey across the country, visiting a wide variety of unique burger outlets. They're on a mission to taste, review, and rank the best burgers India has to offer, leaving no stone unturned.

In their quest, they'll be trying out burgers from popular spots like Burger Singh, Burger Club, and many more exciting and lesser-known burger joints. However, they won't be stopping at the most famous chains like McDonald's, Burger King, and KFC, as their burgers are already well-known and widely reviewed. Instead, FoodieWe focuses on discovering hidden gems and iconic local favorites that truly showcase the diversity and creativity of India's burger scene.

Subscribe to join Onkar, Mukti, and Aditya on their exciting food adventures, where you'll get honest reviews, behind-the-scenes looks at burger-making processes, and plenty of deliciousness. Whether you're a burger enthusiast or just love exploring new flavors, FoodieWe is your go-to channel for the ultimate burger experience in India!

Onkar ka Instagram -  https://www.instagram.com/onkarrandhawa/?hl=en

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: SAZA | King & MC Heam | Monopoly Moves | Official Music Video
snippet.description:
“SAZA'' arrives as the seventh single from KING’s upcoming “Monopoly Moves” album, and marks his debut collaboration with seasoned rapper/singer-songwriter MC Heam. Adorned by an infectious, yet soulful production effort courtesy Exult Yowl, KING and Heam pair up to double down on the enchanting allure of their melodic craftsmanship to deliver a monsoon-friendly groove as they confess their emotions to their love interest while laying down a smooth & memorable hook, while taking a leaf out of the New Delhi-based artist’s knack for creating bittersweet bops.

STREAM NOW : https://out-now.lnk.to/_SAZA

snippet.title: Nita Ambani के लाडले बेटे की शादी के खास इंतजाम |BT Bazaar|
snippet.description:
#news #latestnews #ambanifamily #ambaniwedding #ambanilifestyle 

Anant Ambani-Radhika Merchant Wedding LIVE Updates: Reliance group shared Nita Ambani's video, stating the marriage would be an ‘Ode to Kashi.’ Shah Rukh Khan, Sachin Tendulkar, and other guests including former UK Prime Minister Boris Johnson arrived in Mumbai today morning for the wedding.Watch this video for more Updates.

बिजनेस जगत की हर बड़ी खबर, उनसे जुड़े एक्सप्लेनर वीडियो, बिजनेस शख्सियत  की दिलचस्प कहानियां, रियल एस्टेट, गोल्ड, ऑटो सेक्टर, स्टार्टअप्स,  शेयर बाजार, सेंसेक्स और पर्सलन फाइनेंस जैसे विषयों की जानकारी हासिल करने के लिए जुड़े बिजनेस टुडे हिंदी से। यहां आपकों म्यूचुअल फंड, एसआईपी, इक्विटी, बीमा, लोन्स, पेंशन, रिटायरमेंट योजनाओं के बारे में आसान भाषा में मिलेगी दिलचस्प जानकारी।

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4134 -  Surprise Dekh Khush Hua Popatlal?! I Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

About MaaTri Media 

MaaTri, represents the most beautiful relationship between a mother and a daughter - Nisha Topwal & Anantya Anand aka. MyMissAnand. MaaTri is formed through a combination of two Hindi words - Maa (Mother) and PuTri (daughter) that brings forth energy, enthusiasm and determination to spread positive vibes through their outstanding content. Their content revolves around fashion, food, comedy, parenting, travel, glimpse of their family and simple day-to-day activities that both enjoy doing together.
